pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: header-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 50, 4, 30]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: header-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [76, 48, 300, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 3
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>THE PROBLEM  //  التحديات</p>
  - elementId: title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 90, 600, 50]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      text: |
        <p>تحديات القطاع العقاري</p>
      wrap: false
  - elementId: p1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 170, 370, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E5E5E5"
  - elementId: p1-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 170, 5, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#DC2626"
  - elementId: p1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 195, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>تشتت بيانات العملاء</p>
  - elementId: p1-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 240, 320, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$muted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>بيانات العملاء متفرقة على Excel وWhatsApp وورق — لا يوجد نظام موحد لإدارة العملاء المحتملين</p>
  - elementId: p2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 170, 370, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E5E5E5"
  - elementId: p2-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 170, 5, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#DC2626"
  - elementId: p2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 195, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>ضياع فرص المبيعات</p>
  - elementId: p2-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 240, 320, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$muted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>80% من الفرص تضيع بسبب بطء المتابعة وعدم وجود نظام آلي لتتبع رحلة العميل</p>
  - elementId: p3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 170, 370, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E5E5E5"
  - elementId: p3-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 170, 5, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#DC2626"
  - elementId: p3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 195, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>صعوبة تحليل السوق</p>
  - elementId: p3-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 240, 320, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$muted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>لا توجد أدوات تحليلية لفهم اتجاهات السوق وتسعير الوحدات بشكل تنافسي</p>
  - elementId: p4-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 435, 370, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E5E5E5"
  - elementId: p4-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 435, 5, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#DC2626"
  - elementId: p4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 460, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>الامتثال التنظيمي</p>
  - elementId: p4-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 505, 320, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$muted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>متطلبات PDPL وZATCA تضع ضغطاً إضافياً على الشركات العقارية لحماية بيانات العملاء</p>
  - elementId: stat-box
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 435, 765, 240]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: stat-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [490, 465, 300, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>80%</p>
  - elementId: stat-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [490, 530, 500, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "#FFFFFFCC"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>من فرص المبيعات تضيع بسبب عدم وجود نظام CRM متكامل</p>
